                <div class="row mt-3">
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="skill-box text-center p-4">
                            <i class="fab fa-html5 fa-4x text-warning"></i>
                            <h3 class="mt-3">HTML5</h3>
                            <p class="skill-description">Proficient in semantic HTML5 to create structured, accessible web pages.</p>
                            <div class="progress">
                                <div class="progress-bar bg-warning" style="width: 90%" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="90" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">90%</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="skill-box text-center p-4">
                            <i class="fab fa-css3-alt fa-4x text-primary"></i>
                            <h3 class="mt-3">CSS3</h3>
                            <p class="skill-description">Expert in crafting responsive layouts using Flexbox, Grid, and CSS Variables.</p>
                            <div class="progress">
                                <div class="progress-bar bg-primary" style="width: 90%" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="90" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">90%</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="skill-box text-center p-4">
                            <i class="fab fa-bootstrap fa-4x text-info"></i>
                            <h3 class="mt-3">Bootstrap</h3>
                            <p class="skill-description">Skilled in building responsive and fast-loading websites with Bootstrap's grid system and components.</p>
                            <div class="progress">
                                <div class="progress-bar bg-info" style="width: 90%" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="90" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">90%</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="skill-box text-center p-4">
                            <i class="fab fa-tailwindcss fa-4x text-teal"></i>
                            <h3 class="mt-3">Tailwind CSS</h3>
                            <p class="skill-description">Experience with Tailwind CSS for utility-first design, creating flexible and efficient UIs.</p>
                            <div class="progress">
                                <div class="progress-bar bg-teal" style="width: 90%" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="90" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">90%</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="skill-box text-center p-4">
                            <i class="fab fa-react fa-4x text-blue"></i>
                            <h3 class="mt-3">React</h3>
                            <p class="skill-description">Building dynamic, single-page applications using React, with state management through Redux and Context API.</p>
                            <div class="progress">
                                <div class="progress-bar bg-blue" style="width: 80%" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="80" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">80%</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                      <div class="skill-box text-center p-4">
                          <i class="material-icons md-48 text-primary">design_services</i> <!-- Material UI Icon -->
                          <h3 class="mt-3">Material UI</h3>
                          <p class="skill-description">Building responsive, visually appealing user interfaces using Material UI, focusing on design consistency and ease of use.</p>
                          <div class="progress">
                              <div class="progress-bar bg-warning" style="width: 80%" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="80" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">80%</div>
                          </div>
                      </div>
