                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="skill-box text-center p-4">
                            <i class="fas fa-cloud fa-4x text-primary"></i>
                            <h3 class="mt-3">Cloud Services</h3>
                            <p class="skill-description">Deploying applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Heroku, and DigitalOcean.</p>
                            <div class="progress">
                                <div class="progress-bar bg-primary" style="width: 50%" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="50" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">50%</div>
